content: If you are a fan of any outdoorsy activity or the ocean  - preferably, both at once - Yeongjong Sea Side Rail Bike is a must visit. Can arguably be even better than  riding around near the river on your bike on a sunny Sunday.
I really enjoyed it along the sea road!! It's a little hard to go, but when I come back, I'm very happy and comfortable with the downhill road :)
It's the best! The sea breeze is good and dogs are allowed :)
It's a little unfortunate that it's more modern than it used to be near the neighborhood.
